snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN The Culling Game | Official Teaser | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll January 2026! Watch JUJUTSU KAISEN Crunchyroll! https://got.cr/cc-jjkpv

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

बैटमैन क्लेफेस के पहले लुक का विश्लेषण। नए जोकर के पहले लुक की व्याख्या। बैटमैन के खलनायक के संदर्भ और छिपे हुए विवरण। डीसीयू का नया बैटमैन। बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड, जेम्स गन के साक्षात्कार का विश्लेषण।

सुपरमैन 2025 ईस्टर एग्स और छिपे हुए विवरण जो हमसे छूट गए। मिल्ली एल्कॉक का सुपरगर्ल सीन। नया सुपरमैन बनाम हेनरी कैविल, सुपरमैन में बदलाव। जेम्स गन का नया जस्टिस लीग। फोर्ट्रेस ऑफ़ सॉलिट्यूड, ब्रैडली कूपर जोर-एल कैमियो सीन, केलेक्स रोबोट्स, नए सीन। बैटमैन में नए बदलाव और डीसी मूवीज़ की बैटमैन के लिए योजना की व्याख्या। नए फुटेज और सीन। फोर्ट्रेस ऑफ़ सॉलिट्यूड। सुपरमैन बनाम अल्ट्रामैन, ईविल सुपरमैन। ग्रीन लैंटर्न का पहला लुक। मिस्टर टेरिफिक क्रिप्टो सीन। सुपरमैन बनाम लेक्स लूथर, नए फुटेज, सुपरमैन लिगेसी 2025 का टीज़र। नया सुपरमैन सूट, द फ्लैश रिटर्न्स की व्याख्या। मिली एल्कॉक सुपरगर्ल। नई सुपरगर्ल बनाम पिछले संस्करण। सुपरगर्ल वुमन ऑफ़ टुमॉरो मूवी का टीज़र। डेविड कोरेंसवेट सुपरमैन, निकोलस हॉल्ट लेक्स लूथर की व्याख्या, लेक्स लूथर के पिछले संस्करणों जैसे मैन ऑफ़ स्टील, बैटमैन बनाम सुपरमैन, जस्टिस लीग से बदलाव। द अथॉरिटी। सुपरमैन लिगेसी का कथानक और कहानी की व्याख्या। नई सुपरगर्ल की व्याख्या।

डेविड कोरेंसवेट सुपरमैन, रेचल ब्रोसनाहन लोइस लेन की व्याख्या। बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड का टीज़र और नए बैटमैन की घोषणा अगले साल की जाएगी। बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड का टीज़र और नए बैटमैन की घोषणा अगले साल की जाएगी। नाथन फ़िलियन, ग्रीन लैंटर्न, हॉकगर्ल, मिस्टर टेरिफिक और कई नए जस्टिस लीग किरदार। नया जस्टिस लीग एनिमेटेड जस्टिस लीग टीम पर ज़्यादा क्यों आधारित है?

जेसन मोमोआ लोबो के बारे में बताया गया। हेनरी कैविल, सुपरमैन की भविष्य की योजनाएँ, हटाए गए दृश्य। सुपरमैन लिगेसी, बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड, जेम्स गन, डीसीईयू रीबूट के बारे में बताया गया। जेम्स गन, जस्टिस लीग के कलाकारों को कैसे नए सिरे से चुन रहे हैं।

और भी कई डीसी और मार्वल ट्रेलर आ रहे हैं: सुपरमैन ट्रेलर 2025, एवेंजर्स 5 डूम्सडे ट्रेलर और जल्द ही फैंटास्टिक फोर के और भी ट्रेलर वीडियो!

슈퍼맨 2025 이스터 에그 및 우리가 놓친 숨겨진 디테일. 밀리 알콕의 슈퍼걸 장면. 새로운 슈퍼맨 대 헨리 카빌 슈퍼맨 변화. 제임스 건의 새로운 저스티스 리그. 포트리스 오브 솔리튜드, 브래들리 쿠퍼 조엘 카메오 장면, 켈렉스 로봇, 새로운 장면. 새로운 배트맨 변화와 배트맨을 위한 DC 영화 계획 설명. 새로운 영상과 장면. 포트리스 오브 솔리튜드. 슈퍼맨 대 울트라맨, 사악한 슈퍼맨. 그린 랜턴 첫 등장. 미스터 테리픽 크립토 장면. 슈퍼맨 대 렉스 루터, 새로운 영상, 슈퍼맨 레거시 2025 티저. 새로운 슈퍼맨 슈트, 플래시 리턴즈 설명. 밀리 알콕 슈퍼걸. 새로운 슈퍼걸 대 이전 버전. 슈퍼걸 우먼 오브 투모로우 영화 티저. 데이비드 코렌스윗 슈퍼맨, 니콜라스 홀트 렉스 루터 설명, 맨 오브 스틸, 배트맨 대 슈퍼맨, 저스티스 리그 등 이전 버전의 렉스 루터와의 변화. 어쏘리티. 슈퍼맨 레거시 줄거리 및 스토리 설명. 새로운 슈퍼걸 설명.

데이비드 코렌스윗 슈퍼맨, 레이첼 브로스나한 로이스 레인 설명. 배트맨 브레이브 앤 더 볼드 티저와 새로운 배트맨은 내년에 발표될 예정입니다. 배트맨 브레이브와 대담한 티저, 그리고 새로운 배트맨은 내년에 발표될 예정입니다. 네이선 필리언, 그린 랜턴, 호크걸, 미스터 테리픽 등 새로운 저스티스 리그 캐릭터들이 등장합니다. 새로운 저스티스 리그가 애니메이션 저스티스 리그 팀을 기반으로 하는 이유.

제이슨 모모아 로보에 대한 설명. 헨리 카빌의 슈퍼맨 미래 계획, 삭제 장면. 슈퍼맨 레거시, 배트맨 브레이브와 대담한 제임스 건 DCEU 리부트에 대한 설명. 제임스 건이 저스티스 리그 배우들을 어떻게 재구성하는지

snippet.title: Sergio Ramos - CIBELES (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Sergio Ramos - CIBELES [Official Video]

Escucha "CIBELES" aquí:
https://rimasmusic.io/cibeles

_______________________________________

Escrito por Sergio Ramos.
Producido por Ovy On the Drums y YerayMusic.
Mezclado y masterizado por Mosty. 
Un vídeo musical de Little Spain.


LETRA👇:

Hay cosas que no te dije
Que todavía me duelen 
Yo nunca quise irme 
Tú me pediste que vuele 
Uohohoh
Tú me pediste que vuele
Hmmm
Tú me pediste
Yo mataba por ti
Te amé y te defendí
Pero no estaba en mí 
Tú me pediste que vuele
De gala me vestí
Sangre y sudor te di
Te disfruté y te sufrí
Espero que te vaya bien
Aunque sin ti me siento mal
Menos mal que yo me marché
Porque no me trataste igual
Tú me amaste y yo te amé 
Pero siempre alguien da más
Todo fue como lo soñé
Hasta que tocó despertar
Te puse coronas
Tú me pusiste alas
No sabía que eran solo para que me alejara
Y te miro ahora
Sigues igual de bella
Que nadie es imprescindible la vida te enseña
Un partido dura 90
Y te di 90 y tres más de la cuenta
Nunca me cansé de intentar
Esta historia fue una leyenda
Prefiero morir de pie que vivir arrodillado
Daré el corazón, aunque me lo devuelvan dañado
Espero que te vaya bien
Aunque sin ti me siento mal
Menos mal que yo me marché
Porque no me trataste igual
Tú me amaste y yo te amé 
Pero siempre alguien da más
Todo fue como lo soñé
Hasta que tocó despertar
Te olvidaste de mí
Me dejaste de lado
Sin poder decidir
Eso es lo que más me duele
Y aunque todo fue así
Volvería encantado
Una vez y hasta 1.000
Tú lo sabes, Cibeles

X: https://twitter.com/sergioramos
TIKTOK: https://www.tiktok.com/@sergioramos

snippet.title: Oscar Maydon, Fuerza Regida - Tu Boda (Letra/Lyrics)
snippet.description:
♫ Oscar Maydon, Fuerza Regida - Tu Boda (Letra/Lyrics)

⭐ Download/Stream: 

🎤 Letra: Oscar Maydon, Fuerza Regida - Tu Boda

[Intro: Óscar Maydon]
(Siento un vacío muy frío por dentro, mi amor)
(Cuando te fuiste, te robaste mi corazón)
(Me quedé loco de tanto pensar y pensar)
(Me iré al infierno, pero me tengo que vengar)

[Verso 1: Óscar Maydon & JOP]
Siento un vacío muy frío por dentro, mi amor
Cuando te fuiste, te robaste mi corazón
Me quedé loco de tanto pensar y pensar
Me iré al infierno, pero me tengo que vengar
Quiero manchar el vestido blanco de rojo
Sé que el altar dе Dios es santo, pero, mi amor
Cien invitados y todos tеndrán que mirar
Que nuestro amor, va al más allá

[Coro: Óscar Maydon & JOP]
Quiero que bailemos juntos
En el cielo, el infierno, pero sin ese puto
El que te ha apartado todo este tiempo de mí
Al inconsciente que hizo que no fueras pa' mí
Danza, una danza eterna
Pero me voy contigo, pero no vamos juntos
Llevo tres noches malditas sin poder dormir
Solo pensando y pensando que eres para mí

[Interludio: Óscar Maydon & JOP]
¡Uh!
Me despido de ti para siempre, chiquitita
Ahí le va para todos que traen el corazón roto
Uh
Y su compa Óscar Maydon
Fuerza Regida

[Verso 2: JOP & Óscar Maydon]
Camino lento, me duele la respiración
A mil por hora latidos de mi corazón
En el pasillo me vienen recuerdos, flashbacks
Prometimos que los dos iríamos al altar
Te quito el belo, aceptaste y luego te beso
Ya has consumado los votos sagrados, mi amor
Un frío muy intenso se llevo todo mi ser
Ya no hay razón pa' estar de pie

[Coro: JOP & Óscar Maydon]
Quiero que bailemos juntos
En el cielo, el infierno, pero sin ese puto
El que te ha apartado todo este tiempo de mí
Al inconsciente que hizo que no fueras pa' mí
Danza, una danza eterna
Pero me voy contigo, pero no vamos juntos
Llevo tres noches malditas sin poder dormir
Solo pensando y pensando que eras para mí

[Verso 3: JOP & Óscar Maydon]
Miro como brillan tus ojos
Me resigno perderte y esta vez para siempre
Me arrepentí de quitarte tu felicidad
Te dejaré una familia puedas comenzar
Me despido, me despido pa' siempre
Y te deseo suerte, y bendigo mi muerte
Se la dedico al amor que nunca funcionó
A la persona que roto tienen el corazón

#OscarMaydon #FuerzaRegida #TuBoda #Letra
tags: En el cielo el infierno pero sin ese puto

snippet.description:
✨¡Muchas gracias por ver el video! espero que les haya gustado. ✨

🔔 Activa las notificaciones para enterarte de los nuevos vídeos!

🌟 Sigue a Fuerza Regida por aquí 🌟
🎬 YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@FUERZAREGIDA/videos
📘 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fronteragrupo/?locale=es_LA
📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/grupofrontera/
🎵 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@grupofrontera?lang=es

Antes de ver este vídeo, chequea el original:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UStUu4Ew3SU&ab_channel=FUERZAREGIDA

📝 Letra/ Lyrics:
[Verso 1]
Otra vez otra en mi cama, qué puta ansiedad
Suena el timbre y tú en mi celular
Vieras qué agüite me da contestar
Tú no me entiendes ni me entenderás
Otra vez con pleitos, deja de pelear
Todo lo que hago es por ti nomás
Sabes que te amo, tú eres la especial
Las otras capillas pa' un rato nomás

[Coro]
Pero entiéndeme, mija, es la vida de artista
Me la navego ente loquera, desvergue de güeras
Y nomás la ansiedad no se va

[Interludio]
Válgame, Dios
Fuerza Regida
¿Cómo puedo, mija?

[Verso 2]
Otra vez llorando en el espejo tu vanidad
Nuevamente, concluimos, me quieres cambiar
La historia nunca va a acabar

[Coro]
Pero entiéndeme, mija, es la vida de artista
Me la navego ente loquera, desvergue de güeras
Y nomás la ansiedad no se va (Jaja)

snippet.title: Keane - Somewhere Only We Know (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Keane - Somewhere Only We Know (Lyrics)

Follow Keane:
https://Keane.lnk.to/InstagramID
https://Keane.lnk.to/FacebookID
https://Keane.lnk.to/TwitterID

Lyrics:

[Verse 1]
I walked across an empty land
I knew the pathway like the back of my hand
I felt the earth beneath my feet
Sat by the river and it made me complete

[Refrain]
Oh, simple thing, where have you gone?
I'm getting old and I need something to rely on
So tell me when you're gonna let me in
I'm getting tired and I need somewhere to begin

[Verse 2]
I came across a fallen tree
I felt the branches of it looking at me
Is this the place we used to love?
Is this the place that I've been dreaming of?

[Pre-Chorus]
Oh, simple thing, where have you gone?
I'm getting old and I need something to rely on
So tell me when you're gonna let me in
I'm getting tired and I need somewhere to begin

[Chorus]
And if you have a minute, why don't we go
Talk about it somewhere only we know?
This could be the end of everything
So why don't we go somewhere only we know?

[Post-Chorus]
Somewhere only we know

[Pre-Chorus]
Oh, simple thing, where have you gone?
I'm getting old and I need something to rely on
So tell me when you're gonna let me in
I'm getting tired and I need somewhere to begin

Talk about it somewhere only we know?

So why don't we go? So why don't we go?

Oh

[Chorus]
This could be the end of everything
So why don't we go somewhere only we know?

[Outro]
Somewhere only we know

snippet.title: The Under-Clash | Clash-A-Rama vs. Mash-A-Rama
snippet.description:
Goblins went digging for endless Gold, but found a strange, mashup world beneath our feet! Welcome Mash-A-Rama mayhem to your Village with Under-Hero Skins! These nefarious subterranean tyrants are a wild mix of Troop and Hero! The Mash-A-Rama Scenery turns your Village into a giant loot-grabbing Goblin drill. This unique, scrolling Scenery is full of lost treasures and fun easter eggs! A bunch of fun Events are rising to the surface to make this Season epic from the ground up!


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Minecraft, But Every Minute The Speedrunner Switches...
snippet.description:
Minecraft, But Every Minute The Speedrunner Switches... All we had to do was speedrun and beat Minecraft with a twist...

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @sapnap
➽ Twitch - @sapnap
➽ Instagram - @sapnapinsta

In this challenge me and my friends are essentially one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing

This video was inspired by this video posted here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WU5etmP0h0Y

Dream: ​⁠@dream 
George: ​⁠@GeorgeNotFound 
Daquavis: ​⁠@DaquavisMC 
Shadoune: ​⁠@Shadoune666 

This was a ton of fun, if we get 100,000 likes we will do this again and play until we beat the game no matter what!

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). What is ROBLOX? #Roblox​​​ is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet­-to-­be­-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“ROBUX”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Hollow Knight - Speedrunner vs. 4 Hunters, but there's a Traitor (GRAND FINAL)
snippet.description:
FOLLOW ME FOR SILKSONG: https://www.twitch.tv/fireb0rn https://discord.gg/S6cJBeN

Today, I'm playing Hollow Knight Speedrunner vs. Hunters, but one player is secretly a traitor whose goal is to help me win the game. This time, the Traitor has murder powers, allowing them to switch to the Invisibility skin, and they can use Great Slash which deals double damage. One hunter is also the Mayor, whose role is revealed to all players, and they cannot be voted on, but otherwise has no powers. To start a vote, Hunters must visit Jiji in Dirtmouth to sound the alarm, and if a player is voted guilty, their HP is reduced to 2 and they must leave the team voice chat for the rest of the game. If they're the traitor, they also lose all their special powers. And yes, this might be the last Hollow Knight Speedrunner vs. Hunters ever, so thank you all so much for watching and enjoying the content over the years, and here's to doing it in Silksong eventually, too. I'm going to be streaming Silksong and speedrunning the game, so go follow my channel on Twitch or join my Discord for going live notifications. Now, can I beat The Hollow Knight while four hunters try to stop me, and a Traitor tries to help? Let's find out.

▶ HUNTER CREDITS
@Waasephi (he/him) 
@TheSkribeOfSirkles (she/her) https://www.etsy.com/shop/SirklesStudio
aPress (he/him) https://www.twitch.tv/a_press
cronster (he/him) https://www.twitch.tv/cronster_sr
tsira_kura (they/them) https://www.twitch.tv/tsira_kura

▶ SKINS CREDITS
Student by KAdala
Among Us by 草莓Amon
Among Us (recolors) by Ismoil

▶ OTHER CREDITS
Edited (cuts) by @PyeFive https://www.twitch.tv/pyefive

▶ MODS CREDITS
https://pastebin.com/D9AqK93C

▶ RULES
- Win Condition: The Speedrunner wins by defeating The Hollow Knight. Hunters win if the Speedrunner dies.
- Starting Rules: The Speedrunner has an accelerated start with Forgotten Crossroads 4MS and Vengeful Spirit "complete" and begins from the Ancestral Mound bench. Hunters start simultaneously with the runner, but must each select a starting location from: Mato, Stone Sanctuary, Bretta, Grey Mourner, and Soul Sanctum Toll. Only one hunter per starting location.
- Death Penalty: Hunters must wait in King's Pass for one minute after dying.
- The Speedrunner cannot hear the Hunters except when they are in close proximity.
- Banned Charms: Flukenest, Dashmaster, Great Slash
- Hunter Scaling: Hunters start with 4 HP, Kingsoul, and Grubsong. Hunters gain movement abilities when the Speedrunner does. Hunters gain Vengeful Spirit and a Nail Upgrade with the second movement ability. Hunters gain a Mask Shard for each Speedrunner powerup collected. Powerups are defined as completed masks, soul vessels, charm notches, nail upgrades, nail arts, spells, and spell upgrades. NOTE: Hunters do not gain Mask Shards for powerups obtained from the Speedrunner accelerated start.
- Chat Alerts: When the speedrunner collects a powerup. When the speedrunner collects a movement ability (alert specifies the ability collected). When a toll is purchased. When a shop item is purchased. When a charm is collected. When a lever is hit. When a tram is used. When a grub is rescued. When a boss is defeated. When a stag is used (alert does not specify destination). When a stag is used while a hunter is in the room (alert specifies destination). When the runner dies. When the final boss is defeated.

▶ FOLLOW ME
Stream: https://www.twitch.tv/fireb0rn
Stream VODs: https://youtube.com/@fireb0rnVODs
Bluesky: http://fireb0rn.bsky.social/
Discord: https://discord.gg/S6cJBeN
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fireb0rngg/

▶ MUSIC
Hollow Knight - Gods & Nightmares - Daughter of Hallownest [0:00]
